      "id": "PopularPost237155",
      "post_content": "Why is this rated so high? It's trash. You get 1/1s. Sometimes. Getting three 1/1s from a four mana enchantment doesn't sound like a 3.7 to me at all, more like a 1.5.  \nThe whole point of a color hate card is to be super good against those colors. See [Boil](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boil) or [Justice](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Justice). This card struggles to even return its own value.",
      "posted_by": "Kryptnyt",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost237155\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Why is this rated so high? It's trash. You get 1/1s. Sometimes. Getting three 1/1s from a four mana enchantment doesn't sound like a 3.7 to me at all, more like a 1.5.<br/>The whole point of a color hate card is to be super good against those colors. See <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boil\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boil\">Boil</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Justice\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Justice\">Justice</a>. This card struggles to even return its own value.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '237155'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy24840\">Kryptnyt</span>\r\n                                (4/11/2012 6:38:04 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Ima